      "title": "ROUSSEAU AND HO CHI MINH'S VIEWS ON THE CONSTITUTIONAL AND LAWFUL STATE \u2013 FROM THEORY TO PRACTICE IN VIETNAM",
      "authors": [
        {
          "name": "Nguy\u1ec5n Trung Hi\u1ec3u",
